---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="ZenithVertex mission and focus areas.">
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-[--color-text]">About ZenithVertex</h1>
    <p class="mt-4 text-[--color-text-muted]">
      ZenithVertex is an open-source organization focused on building high-quality software across three core areas.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-10 text-xl font-semibold text-[--color-text]">Our focus</h2>
    <ul class="mt-4 grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2">
      <li class="rounded-lg border border-[--color-border] bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[--color-text]">Web Development</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-[--color-text-muted]">
          Modern, accessible, and performant web experiences built with open standards and mainstream frameworks.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li class="rounded-lg border border-[--color-border] bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[--color-text]">Artificial Intelligence</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-[--color-text-muted]">
          Practical AI tooling and integrations that make developers more productive without adding bloat.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li class="rounded-lg border border-[--color-border] bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[--color-text]">Clean Architecture</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-[--color-text-muted]">
          Maintainable, testable, and well-structured codebases that scale with contributors and feature sets.
        </p>
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="mt-10 text-xl font-semibold text-[--color-text]">Get involved</h2>
    <p class="mt-2 text-[--color-text-muted]">
      We welcome contributors of all backgrounds. Browse our repositories, file issues, or join the discussion on GitHub.
    </p>
    <div class="mt-4">
      <a
        href="https://github.com/ZenithVertex"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="inline-block rounded-lg bg-[--color-primary] px-5 py-3 font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-[--color-primary-dark]"
      >
        View our GitHub repos
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
